), plays an essential role for zygotes to progress beyond the first embryonic cell divisions via regulation of actin dynamics (PubMed:15580268). Required for the centralization of the mitotic spindle and symmetric division of zygotes (By similarity). Plays a role in the regulation of cell morphology and cytoskeletal organization in epithelial cells (PubMed:21834987). Required for the up-regulation of atypical chemokine receptor ACKR2 from endosomal compartment to cell membrane, increasing its efficiency in chemokine uptake and degradation (PubMed:23633677). Required for neural tube morphogenesis and neural crest cell migration (By similarity). {ECO:0000250|UniProtKB:P18760, ECO:0000269|PubMed:11812157, ECO:0000269|PubMed:15580268, ECO:0000269|PubMed:21834987, ECO:0000269|PubMed:23633677}."], "subcellular_locations": [{"location": "Nucleus matrix", "source": "uniprot", "termSL": "SL-0181", "labelSL": "Cellular component"}, {"location": "Cytoplasm", "source": "uniprot", "termSL": "SL-0086", "labelSL": "Cellular component"}, {"location": "Cell projection", "source": "uniprot", "termSL": "SL-0280", "labelSL": "Cellular component"}, {"location": "Plasma membrane", "source": "HPA_main", "termSL": "SL-0039", "labelSL": "Cell membrane"}], "obsolete_symbols": [{"label": "CFL", "source": "HGNC"}], "obsolete_names": [{"label": "cofilin 1 (non-muscle)", "source": "HGNC"}], "protein_ids": [{"id": "P23528", "source": "uniprot_swissprot"}, {"id": "E9PK25", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "E9PLJ3", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "E9PP50", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "E9PQB7", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "E9PS23", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "G3V1A4", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "V9HWI5", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "ENSP00000309629", "source": "ensembl_PRO"}, {"id": "ENSP00000431696", "source": "ensembl_PRO"}, {"id": "ENSP00000432153", "source": "ensembl_PRO"}, {"id": "ENSP00000432155", "source": "ensembl_PRO"}, {"id": "ENSP000004322